AC Technician - MĂśvenpick Hotel Ibn Battuta Gate
19 Apr 2014 08:39 PM - UAE
. The exotic Mövenpick Hotel Ibn Battuta Gate is a Moroccan themed, 5-star hotel. We are looking for a AC technician to join the team. This individual would fully understand the principles of refrigeration & Air Conditioning and apply them in practice. He will regularly inspect air conditioning compressor units and effect maintenance and repairs as necessary, maintain charging equipment, refrigeration test equipment and A/C tools in good condition, ensure cleanliness of work areas and protection of the surrounding area when executing jobs, understand control principles of all A/C systems and regularly test, repair and calibrate. He will also verify building area temperatures and adjust as necessary and record on the plant log sheet, complete major and minor services on A/C units and refrigeration equipment as assigned, maintain a file for completed job sheets to the Engineering Office for inspection, learn and carry out fire brigade duties when assigned, complete the personal daily job record time book accurately and keep ready for inspection, fully comprehend the building automation system operation, understanding the type and location of alarms and functionality of the system, trouble shoot & repair A/C systems w (more...)
